{"title":"老牛","authors":["石枫"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":5,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"老牛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石枫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老牛是一只"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有翅膀的风筝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老牛走在地里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心事重重咀嚼孤独"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或者在沉寂的处所"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凭栏远眺反刍往事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赏日出日落看云卷云舒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总有几分迷惘几分惆怅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡间的田埂和小路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵横交错牵牵连连"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一如那坚韧而绵长的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沾满了草香的线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"断线的可能"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝不可能"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是老牛没有翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老牛没有翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是它向往飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老牛于是一面走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面用犁耙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将自己的脚印一一抹去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同鸟飞过苍穹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了无痕迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老牛没有翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在面朝黄土背朝天的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就把自己的目光栽种在田野里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些水稻高粱小麦玉米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一茬茬在视线上抽芽拔节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到了金风送爽的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些薄明得如蝉翼的清香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就带着老牛的欣慰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘飘飘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘到了天上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老牛没有翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老牛是一只没有翅膀的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风筝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可老牛会"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}